quran[22]{c,v,t,f}:
  54,28,"Na waambie kwamba hakika maji yatagawanywa baina yao; kila sehemu ya maji itahudhuriwa na aliyehusika.",""
  54,29,"Basi wakamwita mtu wao akaja akamchinja.",""
  54,30,"Basi ilikuwaje adhabu yangu na maonyo yangu!",""
  54,31,"Hakika Sisi tuliwatumia ukelele mmoja tu, wakawa kama mabuwa ya kujengea ua.",""
  54,32,"Na bila ya shaka Sisi tumeifanya Qur-ani iwe nyepesi kwa kukumbuka, lakini yupo akumbukaye?",""
  54,33,"Kaumu Lut'i nao waliwakadhibisha Waonyaji.",""
  54,34,"Hakika Sisi tukawatumia kimbunga cha vijiwe, isipokuwa wafuasi wa Lut'i. Hao tuliwaokoa karibu na alfajiri.",""
  54,35,"Kwa neema inayotoka kwetu. Hivyo ndivyo tumlipavyo anayeshukuru.",""
  54,36,"Na hakika yeye aliwaonya adhabu yetu; lakini wao waliyatilia shaka hayo maonyo.",""
  54,37,"Na walimtaka awape wageni wake. Tukayapofua macho yao, na tukawaambia: 'Onjeni basi adhabu na maonyo yangu!'",""
  54,38,"Na iliwafikia wakati wa asubuhi adhabu yangu ya kuendelea.",""
  54,39,"Basi onjeni adhabu na maonyo yangu!",""
  54,40,"Na hakika tumeisahilisha Qur-ani kuikumbuka. Lakini yupo anayekumbuka?",""
  54,41,"Na Waonyaji waliwajia watu wa Firauni.",""
  54,42,"Walizikadhibisha Ishara zetu zote, nasi tukawashika mshiko wa Mwenye nguvu, Mwenye uwezo.",""
  54,43,"Je, makafiri wenu ni bora kuliko hao, au yameandikwa vitabuni kuwa nyinyi hamtiwi makosani?",""
  54,44,"Au ndiyo wanasema: 'Sisi ni wengi tutashinda tu.'",""
  54,45,"Wingi wao huu utashindwa, na wao watasukumwa nyuma.",""
  54,46,"Bali Saa ya Kiyama ndiyo miadi yao, na Saa hiyo ni nzito zaidi na chungu zaidi.",""
  54,47,"Hakika wakosefu wamo katika upotovu na wazimu.",""
  54,48,"Siku watakapokokotwa Motoni kifudifudi waambiwe: 'Onjeni mguso wa Saqar!'",""
  54,49,"Kwa hakika Sisi tumekiumba kila kitu kwa kipimo.",""
